Swiggy is an Indian online food ordering and delivery platform. 
Founded in 2014, Swiggy is headquartered in Bangalore and operates in more than 500 Indian cities as of September 2021.
Besides food delivery, the platform also provides on-demand grocery deliveries under the name Instamart. 
And it is a same-day package delivery service called Swiggy Genie.
It rivals homegrown startup Zomato in food delivery and hyperlocal marketplace.
It is one of the best food deliver app in India.
